The scripts contained in this folder are for generating files related to the documentation.
All assume that flyby has been installed to a system-wide directory/flyby is in PATH.

convert-help-to-manformat.sh: Runs flyby --help and reformats the help to manpage formatting, for pasting into the manpage in ../man/flyby.man.

capture-screenshots.sh: Inputs key sequences to trigger various screens and captures screenshots for the usage guide.
